@startuml sequence_login
!theme plain

title First-Time Login - Browser OAuth Flow

actor User
participant "CommandRouter" as Router
participant "AuthManager" as Auth
participant "Local Callback\nServer" as Callback
participant "System Browser" as Browser
participant "Skills API\n/api/v1/auth" as API
participant "Credential Store" as Store

User -> Router : skills login
Router -> Auth : initiateLogin()

Auth -> Auth : Generate PKCE\ncode_verifier + code_challenge
Auth -> Auth : Generate random state param
Auth -> Callback : Start HTTP server\non 127.0.0.1:<random-port>
Auth -> Browser : Open authorization URL\nwith redirect_uri, state, code_challenge

Browser -> API : GET /authorize\n(user authenticates & consents)
API -> Browser : Redirect to\n127.0.0.1:<port>/callback?code=XXX&state=YYY

Browser -> Callback : GET /callback?code=XXX&state=YYY
Callback -> Auth : Return authorization code

Auth -> Auth : Validate state parameter
Auth -> API : POST /api/v1/auth/token\n{code, code_verifier, redirect_uri}
API --> Auth : {access_token, refresh_token, expires_in}

Auth -> Store : Save StoredCredential
Auth -> Callback : Shutdown server

Auth --> Router : CommandResult(exit_code=0)
Router --> User : "Login successful"

@enduml
